        <source>clearPagination() updating;
/*

Purpose:			Clears the table of all data and removes the pagination params so the table will return to behaving
					like a normal unpaginated table, for cases where the table is reused in different ways

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date				Who		Reason
07 August 2025		jlizm1	Initial creation MTN 35316 Pagination - Work Order Complete

